<http://vocab.linkeddata.es/datosabiertos/def/measure#growthOfPlaces> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The evolution of accommodation capacity over a given period allows us to determine if it is expanding, stable, or declining. It measures the percentage change in accommodation capacity in a certain period with respect to the previous period."@en .
